This is a good app. It is accurate and only takes into value vocal sound and not other sounds like tapping, coughing ect.  However, there's a few things which are missing or needs improvement on the Android version. I will list them below.  1). There is no "Highest" field under "Analysis". I'd like to know my highest vocal frequency.  2). When you select your celebrity matches under "Similar to" and check the distribution comparisons, i.e it says "Yours" and then a celebrities name, it's difficult to identify which line in graph shows your distribution and which one shows the celebrity distribution that you've compared with. The colour code which identifies "Yours" and the celebrity is not accurate.  3). I feel the app takes longer than expected to execute, maybe a good 7+ seconds.  Thank you for your time. Do take my feedback into consideration.
